ification: Excellent writing and editing skills in English Have a basic understanding in SEO and content marketing (preferred) Have a basic understanding or passion in blockchian technology (preferred) Capable of explaining complicated products and processes in simple language to both business partners and consumers. Ability to craft compelling messaging for both technical and non-technical audiences B2B, SaaS and FinTech industries desired. Prior experience in unstructured startup dynamics, which rewards proactive and leadership attitude Ability to communicate effectively and work collaboratively with technical teams Must commit to at least 20 hours each week Note: This position is unpaid and college credits only. "
